snippet.title: Tom Weiland
snippet.description:
Hey, welcome to my channel!

My name is Tom, and I'm a 20 year old game developer. I started teaching myself to code at the age of 12, and I'm currently working on a large multiplayer pirate survival game, and I'm sharing the progress I make in devlogs every few weeks.

I've also put together a networking tutorial series which has been immensely popular, so check that out if it's something you're interested in.

If you'd like to join me on this journey as I build a multiplayer game, consider subscribing and make sure to join the Discord server!

Enjoy the videos :)
Tom
